column2: SELECT TOP # p.ra,p.dec,s.plate,s.mjd,s.fiberid FROM BESTDR7..SpecObj as s 	JOIN BESTDR7..Star AS p ON s.bestObjID = p.objID 	JOIN #x AS x ON x.objID=p.objID JOIN #upload AS u ON u.up_id = x.up_id  WHERE  (s.specClass = dbo.fSpecClass(&&&)) AND p.u > # AND p.g > # AND p.r > # AND p.i > # AND p.z > # AND p.u < # AND p.g < # AND p.r < # AND p.i < # AND p.z < # ORDER BY x.up_id
